{"tid":372774,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"封盤！朱千雪開腔認定醫生男友","createTime":"2017-08-24T14:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T05:03:49.000Z","uid":9573,"like":16,"dislike":149,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b85b50e28cdf9b34f1d191b5d91f033681f0859","tid":372774,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"TVB一班處女黨李亞男、鍾嘉欣、王君馨紛紛嫁人，最近就連女神 朱千雪 亦被踢爆名花有主，有個在澳洲讀醫的男友Justin Ng，一直只表示同男方了解中的她，就向本行獨家開腔，確認醫生男友地位：「我會結婚嘅！」朱千雪更大讚男友：「佢係好男仔嚟！」女神宣布封盤，今次班宅男真係喊出嚟啦！<br />\n<br />\n朱千雪 醫生男友門當戶對<br />\n<br />\n12年港姐季軍朱千雪，有樣有家底兼有學歷，身邊不乏追求者，不過，近日千雪就被爆有個在澳洲讀醫的男友Justin Ng，男方同樣家底豐厚，父親是老牌茶莊「祺棧茶行」老闆，五年前更在香格里拉集團做執行董事，同千雪屋企人係世交，可謂門當戶對！據知千雪同Justin識咗好耐，佢不時會趁放假飛去澳洲探醫生男友，同男友屋企人一樣好friend，吳父都認定咗千雪係新抱仔，成日想個仔可以快啲娶女神入門！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/232680_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F232680_2.jpg&h=3ea84b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪近日為美容院擔任代言人，日前就專登去做脫毛扮靚靚，蜜運中的千雪，唔知係咪因為心情靚食多咗，近日就心曠體胖，連塊面都圓碌碌。雖然有家底，但生活好平實，去完美容院脫毛，就去超市買飲品！<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/232680_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2F232680_4.jpg&h=f8c742cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大方談醫生男友 朱千雪：我會結婚！<br />\n<br />\n朱千雪接受東方新地記者訪問，被問到有冇拍拖，佢話感情事就順其自然，但依家時間唔夠，見面同拍拖都要就時間。提到佢有個醫生男友Justin Ng，千雪甜笑承認：「開名呀！ Justin係好男仔嚟嘅！（做醫生？）係！佢好忙！我都好忙！順其自然啦！（合唔合你杯茶？）合拍嘅！（有冇見家長？）我哋識咗好多年，係family friend嚟！見佢屋企人仲多過見佢！識咗好多好多年，所以先會熟嘅！（幾時會結婚呀？）我會結婚嘅！但唔會諗幾時囉！」首度開腔確認醫生男友地位！"},{"pid":"116d4377d62ba5cf10f61c457bdecda7adc68a62","tid":372774,"uid":9573,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://st.depositphotos.com/1020070/4004/v/950/depositphotos_40040553-stock-illustration-cartoon-tennis-ball-with-a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fst.depositphotos.com%2F1020070%2F4004%2Fv%2F950%2Fdepositphotos_40040553-stock-illustration-cartoon-tennis-ball-with-a.jpg&h=cf24e600&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e4ae869f17ec391eb48c89c9acc161fd5ec1f74","tid":372774,"uid":129273,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:25:19.000Z","msg":"巴打,你要撐住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c796078986bfdd925ee23eaa1a41389ba9d5865","tid":372774,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7f9c43bc587bf53b351f92a29a60329219f1fd","tid":372774,"uid":82532,"like":178,"dislike":3,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://replygif.net/i/759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Freplygif.net%2Fi%2F759.gif&h=54107d82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26ca946e43bf7707ccc7c050d6b56fc51a4f1ef6","tid":372774,"uid":34854,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0170b795a0147602f9161b9c70f5dcbacd0931","tid":372774,"uid":82532,"like":71,"dislike":4,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/k61nOBRRBMxva/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fk61nOBRRBMxva%2Fgiphy.gif&h=736ff3f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c15f1383666c647a27b480cc461d0afd01c54bb","tid":372774,"uid":82532,"like":97,"dislike":3,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.awesomelyluvvie.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Crying-Leonardo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.awesomelyluvvie.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F201